title._content: Summer Street View in Keene New Hampshire

description._content: TITLE Summer Street View in Keene New Hampshire CREATOR Wardwell, Anne, Keene NH SUBJECT Houses - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION "The same features which make Court Street so successful are evident on both Summer and School streets. Because of this and because of their physical relationship, there is strong justification for the creation of an historic district to preserve the character of this entire area."
